1
00:01:08,166 --> 00:01:08,625
Nian Nian

2
00:01:08,791 --> 00:01:10,000
Let's go find Teacher Yu.

3
00:01:10,083 --> 00:01:11,916
Instead of suspecting classmates, it's better to ask the teacher to check the surveillance footage.

4
00:01:11,958 --> 00:01:13,375
Let's see what really happened.

5
00:01:13,708 --> 00:01:15,291
Such an official suggestion.

6
00:01:15,375 --> 00:01:16,166
It must be Chen Changning.

7
00:01:16,166 --> 00:01:17,458
That model student must have told you, right?

8
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:18,500
Alright.

9
00:01:19,208 --> 00:01:19,541
Shasha

10
00:01:19,750 --> 00:01:20,375
You go back to the classroom first.

11
00:01:20,708 --> 00:01:22,291
Jing'an and I will go to the teacher's office.

12
00:01:22,291 --> 00:01:23,041
Okay, let's go.

13
00:01:27,416 --> 00:01:29,375
Didn't we agree to have no secrets?

14
00:01:30,208 --> 00:01:31,875
Why are you still not including me?

15
00:01:42,416 --> 00:01:42,958
Excuse me.

16
00:01:43,583 --> 00:01:44,500
You two are here.

17
00:01:44,583 --> 00:01:45,208
What's the matter?

18
00:01:46,166 --> 00:01:46,791
Teacher.

19
00:01:47,500 --> 00:01:48,916
We still haven't found the Walkman.

20
00:01:49,291 --> 00:01:50,750
We wanted to ask if you could help us.

21
00:01:51,416 --> 00:01:51,958
Teacher.

22
00:01:52,291 --> 00:01:53,041
Last night,

23
00:01:53,041 --> 00:01:55,208
I really did put the Walkman in my backpack.

24
00:01:55,541 --> 00:01:57,083
But I just can't find it today.

25
00:01:57,250 --> 00:01:58,958
I suspect someone took it.

26
00:02:01,208 --> 00:02:02,041
I understand.

27
00:02:03,041 --> 00:02:04,208
Accusing someone of stealing

28
00:02:04,208 --> 00:02:05,333
is not something you can say lightly.

29
00:02:06,208 --> 00:02:07,833
I remember there's surveillance in the back.

30
00:02:08,207 --> 00:02:09,166
How about I find some time

31
00:02:09,541 --> 00:02:10,750
to help you two check it out?

32
00:02:12,541 --> 00:02:13,332
Thank you, Teacher.

33
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,750
I brought this for you, eat it quickly.

34
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:22,332
You really don't have to do this, Nian Nian.

35
00:02:23,332 --> 00:02:25,582
No need to be polite with me, just eat.

36
00:02:26,416 --> 00:02:27,125
These past few days,

37
00:02:27,125 --> 00:02:28,957
you've looked so hungry that your complexion isn't good.

38
00:02:29,500 --> 00:02:30,750
There's still PE class this afternoon.

39
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:31,582
It's easy to faint.

40
00:02:32,916 --> 00:02:33,875
Thank you.

41
00:02:42,250 --> 00:02:44,291
I'm really burning the candle at both ends right now.

42
00:02:45,957 --> 00:02:47,582
Teacher Yu Min went to check the surveillance footage.

43
00:02:47,832 --> 00:02:49,875
If she tells me who did it,

44
00:02:50,666 --> 00:02:52,332
how can I still be classmates with them?

45
00:02:53,832 --> 00:02:54,457
What if

46
00:02:54,791 --> 00:02:56,332
What if that person ends up in my class again?

47
00:02:57,125 --> 00:02:58,166
I would totally break down.

48
00:02:58,666 --> 00:03:00,250
We'd keep running into each other all the time.

49
00:03:00,832 --> 00:03:01,582
It would be so awkward.

50
00:03:03,332 --> 00:03:05,082
I believe the teacher will handle it well.

51
00:03:07,916 --> 00:03:09,707
If I find out who did it,

52
00:03:09,707 --> 00:03:10,875
I definitely won't let them off.

53
00:03:11,666 --> 00:03:12,916
What do you want to do?

54
00:03:13,457 --> 00:03:14,791
You could ask Li Minqiu for help.

55
00:03:14,916 --> 00:03:16,207
Let him stand up for you.

56
00:03:16,250 --> 00:03:16,916
Then in the future,

57
00:03:17,416 --> 00:03:18,541
who would dare do something like this again?

58
00:03:19,250 --> 00:03:20,332
I wouldn't go to him.

59
00:03:21,166 --> 00:03:23,707
We have the big boss of No. 2 High School.

60
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,416
Chen Jing'an is here.

61
00:03:25,791 --> 00:03:26,541
Right, Chen Jing'an?

62
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:29,082
If I find out who it is,

63
00:03:29,082 --> 00:03:30,000
I'll ask them to meet me outside school.

64
00:03:30,166 --> 00:03:31,082
And have you fight them.

65
00:03:31,457 --> 00:03:32,750
Let them see how tough you are.

66
00:03:42,625 --> 00:03:43,416
Oh my god.

67
00:03:43,416 --> 00:03:45,125
This is a bit too much.

68
00:03:45,416 --> 00:03:46,375
I can't finish it either.

69
00:03:46,625 --> 00:03:48,166
Sasha, let's eat together.

70
00:03:49,791 --> 00:03:51,207
What do you mean?

71
00:03:51,541 --> 00:03:52,791
Are you asking me to eat your leftovers?

72
00:03:56,041 --> 00:03:57,500
Are you looking down on me?

73
00:03:57,957 --> 00:03:58,916
Then I'll go buy another portion.

74
00:03:58,916 --> 00:03:59,791
No need, thanks.

75
00:04:05,666 --> 00:04:06,457
Shasha

76
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:07,541
Where is Jing'an?

77
00:04:07,541 --> 00:04:08,457
She's just worried you aren't eating enough.

78
00:04:09,250 --> 00:04:09,832
How about this,

79
00:04:09,916 --> 00:04:11,000
if you want to eat anything else, just tell me.

80
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:11,582
I'll buy it for you.

81
00:04:11,957 --> 00:04:12,625
Do you want a drink?

82
00:04:13,125 --> 00:04:13,875
No need, really.

83
00:04:14,875 --> 00:04:16,125
I don't need your charity.

84
00:04:17,165 --> 00:04:17,833
Shasha

85
00:04:19,125 --> 00:04:20,208
That's not what we meant.

86
00:04:20,208 --> 00:04:21,208
You've misunderstood.

87
00:04:21,458 --> 00:04:22,290
Lately,

88
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:23,915
you've been saving money all the time

89
00:04:24,125 --> 00:04:25,000
and not eating.

90
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:26,750
We're worried you'll hurt your stomach.

91
00:04:27,665 --> 00:04:28,290
You guys...

92
00:04:30,415 --> 00:04:31,290
Chen Jing'an

93
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:33,208
I haven't known you for that long, have I?

94
00:04:33,665 --> 00:04:35,125
Why are you pretending to be so nice?

95
00:04:36,790 --> 00:04:37,333
Shasha

96
00:04:37,625 --> 00:04:38,583
Watch your mouth.

97
00:04:38,583 --> 00:04:40,040
Chen Jing'an is just trying to care about you, but you take it the wrong way.

98
00:04:40,375 --> 00:04:40,958
Yeah.

99
00:04:41,208 --> 00:04:42,540
I just don't know what's good for me.

100
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:44,040
Everything's my fault, okay?

101
00:04:44,165 --> 00:04:45,750
Deng Shasha, what do you want from me?

102
00:04:45,750 --> 00:04:47,333
Shasha, Nian Nian, let's talk this out calmly.

103
00:04:47,333 --> 00:04:48,125
Zhu Nian Nian

104
00:04:49,415 --> 00:04:51,625
Do you remember what you said yesterday?

105
00:04:52,125 --> 00:04:52,750
You said

106
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:54,665
I'm your most important friend.

107
00:04:55,208 --> 00:04:56,540
Yeah, that's right.

108
00:04:56,708 --> 00:04:58,165
You are my most important friend.

109
00:04:59,125 --> 00:05:00,040
And then what?

110
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:02,915
You only say it, but you don't mean it.

111
00:05:03,165 --> 00:05:05,208
Lately, you've been acting like a different person.

112
00:05:05,208 --> 00:05:07,040
You're always hanging out with Chen Jing'an.

113
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,165
It's like you two have some secret.

114
00:05:09,165 --> 00:05:10,583
And you can't tell me about it.

115
00:05:11,290 --> 00:05:13,540
If you don't want to be my friend,

116
00:05:13,875 --> 00:05:15,458
then don't mess with me.

117
00:05:23,415 --> 00:05:25,165
You girls are so complicated.

118
00:05:25,708 --> 00:05:27,250
Is it really such a problem to have one more person?

119
00:06:07,833 --> 00:06:08,458
Here you are.

120
00:06:08,708 --> 00:06:09,375
What's wrong?

121
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,958
You didn't bring your phone, did you?

122
00:06:11,790 --> 00:06:12,415
No, I didn't.

123
00:06:12,415 --> 00:06:13,250
My mom wouldn't let me bring it.

124
00:06:13,333 --> 00:06:14,125
It's okay.

125
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:23,083
I'm telling you, she filmed that on purpose.

126
00:06:25,915 --> 00:06:26,750
The teacher's coming.

127
00:06:41,083 --> 00:06:41,583
Tian Ye.

128
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,625
Are you asking for a beating by giving false information?

129
00:06:43,790 --> 00:06:45,083
Exactly.

130
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,250
Come on, come on.

131
00:06:48,958 --> 00:06:51,125
Let's fight.

132
00:06:58,665 --> 00:06:59,250
Nian Nian.

133
00:06:59,790 --> 00:07:00,833
No matter what others say about you,

134
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:01,665
I'll always support you.

135
00:07:02,915 --> 00:07:04,125
Go back.

136
00:07:07,708 --> 00:07:09,250
Why is everyone acting so weird today?

137
00:07:11,125 --> 00:07:12,125
You're the school beauty.

138
00:07:12,125 --> 00:07:12,458
They all...

139
00:07:12,458 --> 00:07:13,208
They all like to look at you.

140
00:07:13,208 --> 00:07:15,290
It's totally normal.

141
00:07:23,915 --> 00:07:24,333
Nian Nian.

142
00:07:24,833 --> 00:07:25,500
What's going on?

143
00:07:27,250 --> 00:07:28,250
Do you know who did it?

144
00:08:22,708 --> 00:08:23,500
Li Minqiu

145
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,415
You brought your phone to school, huh?

146
00:08:32,375 --> 00:08:32,958
Hand it over.

147
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:36,833
Have you all seen the forum?

148
00:08:37,083 --> 00:08:38,208
It's all over the place.

149
00:08:38,208 --> 00:08:39,416
Is there anyone who hasn't seen it?

150
00:08:40,541 --> 00:08:42,416
What else can Zhu Niannian do besides pretending?

151
00:08:42,916 --> 00:08:44,416
Acting like a diva at the rehearsal.

152
00:08:44,583 --> 00:08:45,708
Making the teacher angry.

153
00:08:46,083 --> 00:08:47,375
Can't even remember her lines.

154
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:49,083
And she still has the nerve to play Juliet.

155
00:08:51,458 --> 00:08:52,666
The air today

156
00:08:52,666 --> 00:08:54,250
feels different from before.

157
00:08:54,875 --> 00:08:55,833
Did you notice?

158
00:08:56,291 --> 00:08:58,750
The loyal sidekick isn't defending her anymore.

159
00:08:58,916 --> 00:09:00,208
She got dumped, I guess.

160
00:09:01,041 --> 00:09:01,583
Yeah.

161
00:09:01,916 --> 00:09:03,166
Look at Chen Jing'an.

162
00:09:03,166 --> 00:09:05,416
She's a great host and Chen Changning's sister.

163
00:09:05,416 --> 00:09:06,208
Her family is well-off too.

164
00:09:06,666 --> 00:09:08,416
She and Zhu Niannian are the same kind of people.

165
00:09:08,708 --> 00:09:11,000
Zhu Niannian is actually smarter than anyone.

166
00:09:11,416 --> 00:09:14,291
She knows how to take advantage of being close to the source.

167
00:09:15,125 --> 00:09:16,041
Some people

168
00:09:16,250 --> 00:09:17,583
no matter how good they are at matchmaking,

169
00:09:17,875 --> 00:09:19,416
still can't compare to Chen Jing'an.

170
00:09:19,583 --> 00:09:20,708
She's going to be the future sister-in-law.

171
00:09:21,291 --> 00:09:22,416
If you keep talking nonsense,

172
00:09:22,458 --> 00:09:23,458
I won't be polite to you.

173
00:09:23,458 --> 00:09:24,041
Deng Shasha.

174
00:09:24,041 --> 00:09:25,791
I just told the truth and you can't handle it.

175
00:09:25,916 --> 00:09:27,041
Chen Jing'an, let go of me.

176
00:09:27,166 --> 00:09:28,666
Come on, I dare you to hit me.

177
00:09:28,666 --> 00:09:30,708
Forget it, Tingting, we're all classmates.

178
00:09:30,708 --> 00:09:31,708
Xinyi, don't hold me back.

179
00:09:31,708 --> 00:09:32,541
Ji Wenting.

180
00:09:32,708 --> 00:09:33,750
Are you jealous of Zhu Niannian?

181
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:35,666
Is that why you spend all day talking bad about her?

182
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:37,833
Don't throw my Xiao Si.

183
00:09:38,416 --> 00:09:39,208
Here, take it back.

184
00:09:42,291 --> 00:09:43,541
Everyone, stop!

185
00:09:44,375 --> 00:09:45,958
Do you want the teacher to come?

186
00:09:46,833 --> 00:09:47,916
Stop making a scene.

187
00:10:24,083 --> 00:10:25,166
Let me show you something.

188
00:10:29,375 --> 00:10:30,625
Why did you bring your phone to school?

189
00:10:30,958 --> 00:10:32,125
I want to show you this.

190
00:10:33,166 --> 00:10:35,041
Everyone with a phone knows about it now.

191
00:10:35,041 --> 00:10:36,791
I wonder who could be so heartless.

192
00:10:37,750 --> 00:10:39,000
They're deliberately targeting our school beauty.

193
00:10:39,916 --> 00:10:41,083
Phones aren't allowed at school.

194
00:10:41,625 --> 00:10:43,000
The student council has the authority to handle this.

195
00:10:45,041 --> 00:10:46,208
I'm also in the student council.

196
00:10:46,500 --> 00:10:47,750
So I need to set an example.

197
00:10:52,958 --> 00:10:54,166
I've been thinking about this all afternoon.

198
00:10:54,666 --> 00:10:55,625
I want to contact the forum moderator.

199
00:10:55,625 --> 00:10:56,791
And get this post deleted.

200
00:10:57,375 --> 00:10:58,291
Has the moderator replied?

201
00:10:58,291 --> 00:10:59,125
No, not yet.

202
00:10:59,125 --> 00:11:00,708
Have you offended anyone recently?

203
00:11:01,791 --> 00:11:03,333
It's not like I haven't offended people.

204
00:11:06,083 --> 00:11:07,625
The name of the person who posted this is

205
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:09,750
Ban Cheng Feng Sha

206
00:11:10,166 --> 00:11:11,958
She posted a lot of those slanderous posts.

207
00:11:11,958 --> 00:11:12,750
What do you all think,

208
00:11:13,375 --> 00:11:15,208
is she working with the person who took the Walkman?

209
00:11:15,333 --> 00:11:16,500
Are they in it together?

210
00:11:16,583 --> 00:11:17,875
Just trying to mess with Zhu Niannian.

211
00:11:19,333 --> 00:11:21,000
I can understand posting things like that,

212
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:23,083
but what's the point of taking the Walkman?

213
00:11:23,333 --> 00:11:24,833
It doesn't really make Niannian lose anything.

214
00:11:24,833 --> 00:11:25,958
Is it really worth stealing something?

215
00:11:28,166 --> 00:11:29,541
So are you still rehearsing in private?

216
00:11:29,750 --> 00:11:30,458
No, I'm not.

217
00:11:30,833 --> 00:11:32,500
Chen Jing'an is preparing to host now.

218
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:33,500
There's not much time left.

219
00:11:34,708 --> 00:11:35,500
Don't worry.

220
00:11:35,875 --> 00:11:37,791
If I really can't memorize it,

221
00:11:37,875 --> 00:11:39,500
I'll just secretly bring it with me during the performance.

222
00:11:39,666 --> 00:11:41,083
I'll listen to it while I act.

223
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,291
Let me help you rehearse.

224
00:11:43,291 --> 00:11:45,500
We've known each other for so long, we have great chemistry.

225
00:11:46,083 --> 00:11:46,916
It's really not necessary.

226
00:11:47,166 --> 00:11:48,958
When did you start being so distant with me?

227
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,708
You used to come to me whenever you needed something.

228
00:11:50,708 --> 00:11:51,708
I was always there with you.

229
00:11:51,750 --> 00:11:53,708
But ever since Chen Jing'an came along,

230
00:11:54,541 --> 00:11:55,708
you go to her for everything.

231
00:11:55,708 --> 00:11:56,958
You never think of me anymore.

232
00:11:57,333 --> 00:11:58,500
She and I are good friends.

233
00:11:58,708 --> 00:12:00,500
Isn't it normal for me to ask her for help?

234
00:12:01,291 --> 00:12:02,083
Yeah.

235
00:12:02,333 --> 00:12:03,583
There's nothing wrong with you asking her.

236
00:12:03,583 --> 00:12:05,208
You two are the ones who belong in the same world.

237
00:12:05,666 --> 00:12:06,750
I'm just being petty.

238
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:08,750
I shouldn't be getting in between you two and causing trouble.

239
00:12:13,208 --> 00:12:13,958
Could it be

240
00:12:14,208 --> 00:12:14,958
Deng Shasha

241
00:12:16,333 --> 00:12:17,041
Who

242
00:12:17,291 --> 00:12:18,000
Hello, everyone

243
00:12:18,625 --> 00:12:19,750
The student council would like to remind everyone

244
00:12:20,375 --> 00:12:22,041
Please be sure to follow school rules while on campus

245
00:12:22,625 --> 00:12:23,458
While on campus

246
00:12:23,833 --> 00:12:25,166
It is not allowed to have mobile phones at school

247
00:12:25,166 --> 00:12:26,958
The student council will be increasing inspections soon

248
00:12:27,833 --> 00:12:29,208
Please follow the school rules

249
00:12:29,375 --> 00:12:30,458
If a mobile phone is found

250
00:12:31,166 --> 00:12:32,791
It will be confiscated and handed over to your parents

251
00:12:33,333 --> 00:12:34,458
And you will receive a verbal warning

252
00:12:35,666 --> 00:12:36,583
Thank you for your cooperation

253
00:12:37,541 --> 00:12:38,333
Listen to that

254
00:12:38,833 --> 00:12:40,291
Chen Changning is starting to give orders

255
00:12:40,291 --> 00:12:41,583
Mobile phones are now banned

256
00:12:41,833 --> 00:12:43,791
Is that his order? That's a school rule

257
00:12:47,291 --> 00:12:48,333
Where is Li Minqiu?

258
00:12:48,583 --> 00:12:49,416
It's good that she's not here.

259
00:12:50,916 --> 00:12:52,083
Don't you think

260
00:12:52,416 --> 00:12:54,625
that recently Chen Changning and you—

261
00:12:54,666 --> 00:12:55,583
the fake Zhu Niannian—

262
00:12:55,708 --> 00:12:56,750
have been getting really close?

263
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:58,541
Does he like Zhu Niannian?

264
00:12:58,541 --> 00:12:59,458
Absolutely not.

265
00:13:00,666 --> 00:13:02,666
Niannian is just pretending to be his sister every day.

266
00:13:02,666 --> 00:13:03,875
It's normal for him to help her.

267
00:13:04,875 --> 00:13:05,708
Wrong.

268
00:13:06,041 --> 00:13:07,166
Completely wrong.

269
00:13:07,875 --> 00:13:08,875
As for Chen Changning,

270
00:13:08,875 --> 00:13:10,333
he doesn't know about you two switching places.

271
00:13:10,708 --> 00:13:12,083
Right now, you are Zhu Niannian,

272
00:13:12,666 --> 00:13:14,166
the one everyone at school is talking about.

273
00:13:14,458 --> 00:13:15,250
Not Chen Jing'an.

274
00:13:15,625 --> 00:13:16,500
You get the logic, right?

275
00:13:17,500 --> 00:13:19,166
Now Chen Changning is holding a megaphone,

276
