567
00:26:11,666 --> 00:26:13,208
Misunderstanding, misunderstanding, misunderstanding.

568
00:26:14,541 --> 00:26:16,625
I’m standing up for you right now.

569
00:26:17,208 --> 00:26:18,500
But you keep saying it’s a misunderstanding.

570
00:26:18,916 --> 00:26:20,500
So I’m the one being overly sentimental, huh?

571
00:26:20,666 --> 00:26:22,125
I guess I deserve to be upset, then.

572
00:26:23,000 --> 00:26:24,500
Anyway, she didn’t betray me.

573
00:26:24,583 --> 00:26:25,666
