574
00:26:26,166 --> 00:26:26,833
You guys...

575
00:26:27,041 --> 00:26:28,083
Do whatever you want.

576
00:26:49,291 --> 00:26:50,083
Alright, class.

577
00:26:50,416 --> 00:26:51,458
Let’s look at this problem.

578
00:26:52,666 --> 00:26:54,375
Last time on the test,

579
00:26:54,625 --> 00:26:56,041
