00:27:05,250 --> 00:27:07,875
Label the three white ping pong balls as 1, 2, and 3.

583
00:27:08,625 --> 00:27:12,083
Randomly pick three balls from the six as the basic event.

584
00:27:42,916 --> 00:27:43,791
