710
00:34:08,250 --> 00:34:08,791
Come in.

711
00:34:10,583 --> 00:34:11,166
Junior.

712
00:34:11,416 --> 00:34:12,083
Do you need something?

713
00:34:12,541 --> 00:34:13,708
Teacher Shi said

714
00:34:13,708 --> 00:34:15,375
