715
00:34:15,541 --> 00:34:16,666
It's with the student council.

716
00:34:17,333 --> 00:34:18,333
She asked me to come get it.

717
00:34:19,583 --> 00:34:20,291
I remember.

718
00:34:20,291 --> 00:34:21,125
Let me find it for you.

719
00:34:22,625 --> 00:34:24,583
You're the one who won first place in our school's speech contest.

720
00:34:26,166 --> 00:34:26,916
Yes.

721
00:34:27,208 --> 00:34:28,000
That's me.

722
00:34:29,125 --> 00:34:30,208
